# Commit style

- Follow [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/): `feat:`, `fix:`, `docs:`, `refactor:`, `test:`, `chore:`.
- Use squash merge for PRs — no merge commits.
- Branch naming: `<type>/<slug>` (e.g. `feat/mcp-tool-support`).
